claim.claim-text:
1. A method for a printer apparatus to provide personalized print items, the printer apparatus executing steps comprising: 
receiving data from a portable memory device; 
prompting an operator to select a product template resident in the printer apparatus; 
prompting the operator to select at least one field entry from the data; 
assembling the field entry into the product template; and 
printing the resultant personalized print item.

16. A method for a printer system to provide personalized print items, the printer system apparatus executing steps comprising: 
accessing a portable memory device; 
receiving data from the portable memory device; 
assembling the data into a pre-stored product template found in the printer system; and 
printing the resultant personalized print item.
